  "subject": "Fix basic_vm_macro callback race condition",
  "commit_message": "Fix basic_vm_macro callback race condition\n\n- remove async flag for SDNC callback listener\n- this will likely fix the issue that camunda is often slower\n  to spin up the async thread than SDNC is to handle the request\n  and call the callback\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4270\nChange-Id: I1398cb2f5a029a55f5c4571d98e0f0d2f22c934a\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
